{
  "stem": "6719.9",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And in German, it sounds rougher than in English, believe me.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I was-- they shook my hands afterwards.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I said, you know something?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "You might be lawyers, but to me, it's like a piece of shit that you shake now.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Anyhow, oh, we're coming to Canada.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I said, tell me when you're coming.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I said, I'll give you a good time.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I'll throw you over Niagara Falls.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But in essence, it's stupid that I talk like that because it's their job.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "It's a lawyer's job.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But if it affects you directly, you get angry.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "That's all.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Didn't bother me, I don't think so.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It didn't bother me.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Well, I was coming back.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I worked at Loblaw's at that time.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And no, not at Kuehneman, but when we went to [?",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Zegan, ?] you know.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And then I had a stroke.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I was sitting behind my desk.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "We had a meeting.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And I just slowly fell off the-- off the chair.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And then, all of a sudden-- I was only out, I think, 30 or 40 seconds, which is very good.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "So, you know, it was good for me, anyhow.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "So they put me back into my chair.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And I didn't know what it was.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I mean, how the hell-- how does anybody know if he has a stroke?",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You don't learn this in a packaging course.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And so I sat there, and I phoned my doctor.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And my doctor said to take-- to-- to-- to call an ambulance and get me in there.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But I'm too stubborn, so I phoned Claire first.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I said, honey, I don't take an ambulance.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I'll have somebody drive me there, and I'll pick you up.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I went here first, and then I went to the hospital, to the Queens Bay Hospital down there.",
      "word_count": 19
    }
  ],
